<div id="outline-container-org1ee47c1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org1ee47c1">Ejecutar el Proyecto</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org1ee47c1">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><p>
Inicia el servidor de desarrollo:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-bash">   python manage.py runserver
</pre>
</div></li>

<li>Abre tu navegador en <a href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/">http://127.0.0.1:8000/</a>.</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgdb76eee" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgdb76eee">¡Listo!</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgdb76eee">
<p>
Con esto, tendrás una aplicación funcional para la gestión de personas utilizando Django y PostgreSQL.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>



<div id="outline-container-org0a4b568" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org0a4b568">Lectura de datos de un sensor con Arduino y Raspberry Pi</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org0a4b568">
<p>
Este apartado proporciona una guía para leer datos de un sensor
utilizando Arduino, enviarlos a una Raspberry Pi y visualizarlos en
una interfaz web desarrollada con Django.
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgd63c3ef" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgd63c3ef">Hardware y software necesarios</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgd63c3ef">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><b><b>Hardware</b></b>:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Arduino Uno o similar.</li>
<li>Raspberry Pi (cualquier modelo compatible).</li>
<li>Sensor (por ejemplo, DHT11 o DHT22 para temperatura y humedad).</li>
<li>Cables y protoboard.</li>
</ul></li>

<li><b><b>Software</b></b>:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Arduino IDE.</li>
<li>Python 3 en Raspberry Pi.</li>
<li>Django (framework web).</li>
<li>Biblioteca para el sensor (instalada en Arduino y/o Raspberry Pi).</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org6f60f22" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org6f60f22">Paso 1: Configurar Arduino para leer el sensor</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org6f60f22">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li>Conecta el sensor al Arduino según el esquema del fabricante.</li>
<li><p>
Escribe el código para leer el sensor y enviar los datos por el puerto serie:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-cpp"><span style="color: #86e1fc; font-weight: bold;">   #include</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">&lt;</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">DHT.h</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">&gt;</span>

<span style="color: #86e1fc; font-weight: bold;">   #define</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">DHTPIN</span> 2     <span style="color: #7a88cf;">// </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Pin donde est&#225; conectado el sensor</span>
<span style="color: #86e1fc; font-weight: bold;">   #define</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">DHTTYPE</span> DHT11 <span style="color: #7a88cf;">// </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Cambiar a DHT22 si usas ese modelo</span>

   <span style="color: #ffc777;">DHT</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">dht</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>DHTPIN, DHTTYPE<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>;

   <span style="color: #ffc777;">void</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">setup</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">{</span>
       Serial.begin<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>9600<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>;
       dht.begin<span style="color: #ff995e;">()</span>;
   <span style="color: #c099ff;">}</span>

   <span style="color: #ffc777;">void</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">loop</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">{</span>
       <span style="color: #ffc777;">float</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">temperatura</span> = dht.readTemperature<span style="color: #ff995e;">()</span>;
       <span style="color: #ffc777;">float</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">humedad</span> = dht.readHumidity<span style="color: #ff995e;">()</span>;

       <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> <span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>isnan<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span>temperatura<span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span> || isnan<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span>humedad<span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span> <span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span>
           Serial.println<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"Error al leer el sensor"</span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span>;
           <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span>;
       <span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span>

       Serial.print<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"Temperatura: "</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>;
       Serial.print<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>temperatura<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>;
       Serial.print<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"&#176;C  Humedad: "</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>;
       Serial.print<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>humedad<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>;
       Serial.println<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"%"</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>;

       delay<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>2000<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>; <span style="color: #7a88cf;">// </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Enviar datos cada 2 segundos</span>
   <span style="color: #c099ff;">}</span>
</pre>
</div></li>
<li>Sube este código al Arduino usando el Arduino IDE.</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org4ab6a42" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org4ab6a42">Paso 2: Configurar Raspberry Pi para recibir datos</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org4ab6a42">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><p>
Instala las bibliotecas necesarias en la Raspberry Pi:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   sudo apt update
   sudo apt install python3-pip
   pip3 install pyserial
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Crea un script para leer los datos enviados por el Arduino:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> serial

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">leer_datos_serial</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">puerto</span> = serial.Serial<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'/dev/ttyUSB0'</span>, 9600<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>  <span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Ajusta el puerto seg&#250;n corresponda</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">while</span> <span style="color: #ff995e;">True</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  datos = puerto.readline<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>.decode<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'utf-8'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>.strip<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">print</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>datos<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">__name__</span> == <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"__main__"</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  leer_datos_serial<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
</pre>
</div></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgaeee240" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgaeee240">Paso 3: Configurar Django para mostrar los datos</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgaeee240">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><p>
Crea un nuevo proyecto Django:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   django-admin startproject proyecto_sensor
   <span style="color: #c099ff;">cd</span> proyecto_sensor
   python manage.py startapp sensor
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Crea un modelo en `sensor/models.py` para almacenar los datos del sensor:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.db <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> models

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">class</span> <span style="color: #ffc777;">LecturaSensor</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>models.Model<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">temperatura</span> = models.FloatField<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">humedad</span> = models.FloatField<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">fecha_hora</span> = models.DateTimeField<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>auto_now_add=<span style="color: #ff995e;">True</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">__str__</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> f<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"</span>{<span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span>.fecha_hora}<span style="color: #c3e88d;">: </span>{<span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span>.temperatura}<span style="color: #c3e88d;">&#176;C, </span>{<span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span>.humedad}<span style="color: #c3e88d;">%"</span>
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Realiza las migraciones:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   python manage.py makemigrations
   python manage.py migrate
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Crea una vista en `sensor/views.py` para mostrar las lecturas:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.shortcuts <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> render
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> .models <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> LecturaSensor

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">mostrar_lecturas</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">lecturas</span> = LecturaSensor.objects.<span style="color: #c099ff;">all</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>.order_by<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'-fecha_hora'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)[</span>:10<span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> render<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'sensor/lecturas.html'</span>, <span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'lecturas'</span>: lecturas<span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Configura las URLs en `sensor/urls.py`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.urls <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> path
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> . <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> views

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">urlpatterns</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">''</span>, views.mostrar_lecturas, name=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">'mostrar_lecturas'</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div>

<p>
Y registra las URLs en `proyecto<sub>sensor</sub>/urls.py`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.urls <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> path, include

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">urlpatterns</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'admin/'</span>, admin.site.urls<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">''</span>, include<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'sensor.urls'</span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Crea una plantilla HTML en `templates/sensor/lecturas.html`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">   &lt;<span style="color: #c099ff;">!DOCTYPE</span> html&gt;
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">html</span>&gt;
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">head</span>&gt;
       &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">title</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Lecturas del Sensor</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">title</span>&gt;
   &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">head</span>&gt;
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">body</span>&gt;
       &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">&#218;ltimas Lecturas</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span>&gt;
       &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">table</span>&gt;
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">tr</span>&gt;
               &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;Fecha y Hora&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;
               &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;Temperatura (&#176;C)&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;
               &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;Humedad (%)&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;
           &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">tr</span>&gt;
           {% for lectura in lecturas %}
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">tr</span>&gt;
               &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;{{ lectura.fecha_hora }}&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;
               &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;{{ lectura.temperatura }}&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;
               &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;{{ lectura.humedad }}&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;
           &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">tr</span>&gt;
           {% endfor %}
       &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">table</span>&gt;
   &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">body</span>&gt;
   &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">html</span>&gt;
</pre>
</div></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org72afe47" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org72afe47">Paso 4: Integrar Raspberry Pi con Django</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org72afe47">
<p>
Crea un script para guardar las lecturas del sensor en la base de datos Django:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> serial
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> requests

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">URL</span> = <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/guardar_lectura/"</span>  <span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Cambia seg&#250;n tu configuraci&#243;n</span>

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">enviar_datos</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">puerto</span> = serial.Serial<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'/dev/ttyUSB0'</span>, 9600<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">while</span> <span style="color: #ff995e;">True</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  datos = puerto.readline<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>.decode<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'utf-8'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>.strip<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"Temperatura"</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">in</span> datos <span style="color: #c099ff;">and</span> <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"Humedad"</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">in</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">datos</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">temperatura</span>, <span style="color: #ff98a4;">humedad</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">float</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>x.split<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">": "</span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">)[</span>1<span style="color: #ff98a4;">]</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">for</span> x <span style="color: #c099ff;">in</span> datos.split<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"  "</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">response</span> = requests.post<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>URL, data=<span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'temperatura'</span>: temperatura, <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'humedad'</span>: humedad<span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">print</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>response.status_code, response.reason<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">__name__</span> == <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"__main__"</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  enviar_datos<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgd7c3741" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgd7c3741">Probar el sistema completo</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgd7c3741">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><p>
Inicia el servidor de desarrollo de Django:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   python manage.py runserver
</pre>
</div></li>

<li>Ejecuta el script de la Raspberry Pi para enviar datos.</li>

<li>Abre el navegador y ve a `<a href="http://127.0.0.1:8000">http://127.0.0.1:8000</a>` para ver las lecturas.</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>


<div id="outline-container-org30cc996" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org30cc996">Proyecto Completo Arduino</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org30cc996">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org6db47f8" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org6db47f8">Configuración inicial del proyecto</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org6db47f8">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-orgf177392" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgf177392">Crear el proyecto y la aplicación</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgf177392">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-bash">django-admin startproject gestion_sensores
<span style="color: #c099ff;">cd</span> gestion_sensores
python manage.py startapp sensores
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org2e9144f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org2e9144f">Configuración de aplicaciones en settings.py</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org2e9144f">
<p>
Edite el archivo `gestion<sub>sensores</sub>/settings.py` para agregar la aplicación.
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #ff98a4;">INSTALLED_APPS</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   ...
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'sensores'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'django.contrib.staticfiles'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'django.contrib.sessions'</span>,
<span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org019b0e0" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org019b0e0">Configuración de la base de datos</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org019b0e0">
<p>
Usaremos SQLite por simplicidad, que ya está configurada por defecto.
</p>

<p>
&#x2014;
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org13f5ce6" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org13f5ce6">Modelos</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org13f5ce6">
<p>
Cree el archivo `sensores/models.py` para definir los modelos de usuario y datos del sensor.
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.db <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> models
<span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.contrib.auth.models <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> User

<span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Modelo de datos del sensor</span>
<span style="color: #c099ff;">class</span> <span style="color: #ffc777;">SensorData</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>models.Model<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ff98a4;">usuario</span> = models.ForeignKey<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>User, on_delete=models.CASCADE<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   fecha_hora = models.DateTimeField<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>auto_now_add=<span style="color: #ff995e;">True</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   valor = models.FloatField<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">__str__</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> f<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"</span>{<span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span>.usuario.username}<span style="color: #c3e88d;"> - </span>{<span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span>.valor}<span style="color: #c3e88d;"> - </span>{<span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span>.fecha_hora}<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"</span>
</pre>
</div>

<p>
&#x2014;
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org4d3d384" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org4d3d384">Formularios</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org4d3d384">
<p>
Cree un archivo `sensores/forms.py` para manejar los formularios de entrada.
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> forms
<span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> .models <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> SensorData

<span style="color: #c099ff;">class</span> <span style="color: #ffc777;">SensorDataForm</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>forms.ModelForm<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">class</span> <span style="color: #ffc777;">Meta</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   model = SensorData
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #ff98a4;">fields</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'valor'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div>

<p>
&#x2014;
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgc196b49" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgc196b49">Vistas</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgc196b49">
<p>
Implemente las vistas en `sensores/views.py` para manejar las operaciones de login, altas, bajas, modificaciones y consultas.
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.shortcuts <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> render, redirect, get_object_or_404
<span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.contrib.auth <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> login, logout, authenticate
<span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.contrib.auth.decorators <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> login_required
<span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> .models <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> SensorData
<span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> .forms <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> SensorDataForm

<span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Login</span>
<span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">login_view</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> request.method == <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'POST'</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   username = request.POST<span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'username'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   password = request.POST<span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'password'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   user = authenticate<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, username=username, password=password<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> user:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   login<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, user<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> redirect<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'listar_datos'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">else</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> render<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'login.html'</span>, <span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'error'</span>: <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'Credenciales inv&#225;lidas'</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> render<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'login.html'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>

<span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Logout</span>
<span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">logout_view</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   logout<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> redirect<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'login'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>

<span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Listar datos del sensor</span>
<span style="color: #ffc777;">@login_required</span>
<span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">listar_datos</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   datos = SensorData.objects.<span style="color: #c099ff;">filter</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>usuario=request.user<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> render<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'listar_datos.html'</span>, <span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'datos'</span>: datos<span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>

<span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Crear dato del sensor</span>
<span style="color: #ffc777;">@login_required</span>
<span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">crear_dato</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> request.method == <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'POST'</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   form = SensorDataForm<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request.POST<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> form.is_valid<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   sensor_data = form.save<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>commit=<span style="color: #ff995e;">False</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   sensor_data.usuario = request.user
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   sensor_data.save<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> redirect<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'listar_datos'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">else</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   form = SensorDataForm<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> render<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'crear_dato.html'</span>, <span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'form'</span>: form<span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>

<span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Editar dato del sensor</span>
<span style="color: #ffc777;">@login_required</span>
<span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">editar_dato</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, <span style="color: #c099ff;">id</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   dato = get_object_or_404<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>SensorData, <span style="color: #c099ff;">id</span>=<span style="color: #c099ff;">id</span>, usuario=request.user<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> request.method == <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'POST'</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   form = SensorDataForm<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request.POST, instance=dato<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> form.is_valid<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   form.save<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> redirect<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'listar_datos'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">else</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   form = SensorDataForm<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>instance=dato<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> render<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'editar_dato.html'</span>, <span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'form'</span>: form<span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>

<span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Eliminar dato del sensor</span>
<span style="color: #ffc777;">@login_required</span>
<span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">eliminar_dato</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, <span style="color: #c099ff;">id</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   dato = get_object_or_404<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>SensorData, <span style="color: #c099ff;">id</span>=<span style="color: #c099ff;">id</span>, usuario=request.user<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   dato.delete<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> redirect<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'listar_datos'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
</pre>
</div>

<p>
&#x2014;
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org8ef702c" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org8ef702c">URLs</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org8ef702c">
<p>
Defina las rutas en `sensores/urls.py`.
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.urls <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> path
<span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> . <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> views

<span style="color: #ff98a4;">urlpatterns</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'login/'</span>, views.login_view, name=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">'login'</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'logout/'</span>, views.logout_view, name=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">'logout'</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">''</span>, views.listar_datos, name=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">'listar_datos'</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'crear/'</span>, views.crear_dato, name=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">'crear_dato'</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'editar/&lt;int:id&gt;/'</span>, views.editar_dato, name=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">'editar_dato'</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'eliminar/&lt;int:id&gt;/'</span>, views.eliminar_dato, name=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">'eliminar_dato'</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div>

<p>
Configure el archivo principal de URLs en `gestion<sub>sensores</sub>/urls.py`.
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.contrib <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> admin
<span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.urls <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> path, include

<span style="color: #ff98a4;">urlpatterns</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'admin/'</span>, admin.site.urls<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">''</span>, include<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'sensores.urls'</span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div>

<p>
&#x2014;
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org4a4f377" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org4a4f377">Plantillas HTML</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org4a4f377">
<p>
Cree una carpeta `templates/sensores/` y añada las plantillas necesarias.
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgdd3defb" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgdd3defb">`login.html`</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgdd3defb">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">h2</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; text-decoration: underline;">Iniciar Sesi&#243;n</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">h2</span>&gt;
&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">form</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">method</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"post"</span>&gt;
    {% csrf_token %}
    &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">for</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"username"</span>&gt;Usuario:&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">input</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"text"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">name</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"username"</span> required&gt;
    &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">for</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"password"</span>&gt;Contrase&#241;a:&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">input</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"password"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">name</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"password"</span> required&gt;
    &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"submit"</span>&gt;Entrar&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span>&gt;
    {% if error %}
        &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">p</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">style</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"color: red;"</span>&gt;{{ error }}&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">p</span>&gt;
    {% endif %}
&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">form</span>&gt;
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgca65dd1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgca65dd1">`listar<sub>datos.html</sub>`</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgca65dd1">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">h2</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; text-decoration: underline;">Datos del Sensor</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">h2</span>&gt;
&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"{% url 'crear_dato' %}"</span>&gt;Agregar Dato&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;
&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">table</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">tr</span>&gt;
        &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;Fecha&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;
        &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;Valor&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;
        &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;Acciones&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">th</span>&gt;
    &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">tr</span>&gt;
    {% for dato in datos %}
    &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">tr</span>&gt;
        &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;{{ dato.fecha_hora }}&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;
        &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;{{ dato.valor }}&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;
        &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;
            &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"{% url 'editar_dato' dato.id %}"</span>&gt;Editar&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;
            &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"{% url 'eliminar_dato' dato.id %}"</span>&gt;Eliminar&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;
        &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">td</span>&gt;
    &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">tr</span>&gt;
    {% endfor %}
&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">table</span>&gt;
&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"{% url 'logout' %}"</span>&gt;Cerrar Sesi&#243;n&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgfdb40fb" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgfdb40fb">`crear<sub>dato.html</sub>` y `editar<sub>dato.html</sub>`</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgfdb40fb">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">h2</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; text-decoration: underline;">{% if form.instance.id %}Editar Dato{% else %}Crear Dato{% endif %}</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">h2</span>&gt;
&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">form</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">method</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"post"</span>&gt;
    {% csrf_token %}
    {{ form.as_p }}
    &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"submit"</span>&gt;Guardar&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span>&gt;
&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">form</span>&gt;
</pre>
</div>

