<div id="outline-container-org82d539a" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org82d539a">Integración con Arduino</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org82d539a">
<p>
Para enviar datos desde Arduino, puedes usar una biblioteca como `WiFi.h` o `Ethernet.h` para enviar datos mediante HTTP POST a tu API de Django.
</p>

<p>
Ejemplo de código Arduino:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-cpp"><span style="color: #86e1fc; font-weight: bold;">#include</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">&lt;</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">WiFi.h</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">&gt;</span>
<span style="color: #86e1fc; font-weight: bold;">#include</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">&lt;</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">HTTPClient.h</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">&gt;</span>

<span style="color: #c099ff;">const</span> <span style="color: #ffc777;">char</span>* <span style="color: #ff98a4;">ssid</span> = <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"TuSSID"</span>;
<span style="color: #c099ff;">const</span> <span style="color: #ffc777;">char</span>* <span style="color: #ff98a4;">password</span> = <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"TuPassword"</span>;

<span style="color: #ffc777;">void</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">setup</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">{</span>
  Serial.begin<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>115200<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>;
  WiFi.begin<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>ssid, password<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>;
  <span style="color: #c099ff;">while</span> <span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>WiFi.status<span style="color: #ff98a4;">()</span> != WL_CONNECTED<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span> <span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span>
    delay<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span>1000<span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span>;
    Serial.println<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"Conectando..."</span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span>;
  <span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span>
  Serial.println<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"Conectado al WiFi"</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>;
<span style="color: #c099ff;">}</span>

<span style="color: #ffc777;">void</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">loop</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">{</span>
  <span style="color: #c099ff;">if</span> <span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>WiFi.status<span style="color: #ff98a4;">()</span> == WL_CONNECTED<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span> <span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span>
    <span style="color: #ffc777;">HTTPClient</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">http</span>;
    http.begin<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"http://tu_dominio.com/crear/"</span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span>; <span style="color: #7a88cf;">// </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Cambia por tu URL</span>
    http.addHeader<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"Content-Type"</span>, <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"application/json"</span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span>;

    <span style="color: #ffc777;">float</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">sensorValue</span> = analogRead<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span>A0<span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span>;
    <span style="color: #ffc777;">String</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">postData</span> = <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"{\"valor\":"</span> + String<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span>sensorValue<span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span> + <span style="color: #c3e88d;">"}"</span>;

    <span style="color: #ffc777;">int</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">httpResponseCode</span> = http.POST<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span>postData<span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span>;
    Serial.println<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">"Respuesta HTTP: "</span> + String<span style="color: #b4f9f8;">(</span>httpResponseCode<span style="color: #b4f9f8;">)</span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span>;
    http.end<span style="color: #ff98a4;">()</span>;
  <span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span>
  delay<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span>5000<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>; <span style="color: #7a88cf;">// </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Cada 5 segundos</span>
<span style="color: #c099ff;">}</span>
</pre>
</div>

<p>
&#x2014;
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgac27771" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgac27771">Pruebas y ejecución</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgac27771">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org7f5e55b" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org7f5e55b">Migraciones</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org7f5e55b">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-bash">python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgc2c3f47" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgc2c3f47">Crear superusuario</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgc2c3f47">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-bash">python manage.py createsuperuser
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org5ca917c" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org5ca917c">Iniciar servidor</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org5ca917c">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-bash">python manage.py runserver
</pre>
</div>

<p>
Accede a `/login/` para comenzar a usar el sistema.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>


<div id="outline-container-org71396f8" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org71396f8">Integrando Bootstrap en un Proyecto de Django</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org71396f8">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org0ad749d" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org0ad749d">Introducción</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org0ad749d">
<p>
Bootstrap es una biblioteca de front-end que facilita el diseño de
interfaces web responsivas y modernas. Este apartado muestra cómo
integrarlo en un proyecto de Django.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org8332986" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org8332986">Prerrequisitos</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org8332986">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Tener instalado Django en tu entorno.</li>
<li>Tener un proyecto de Django creado.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgd116df7" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgd116df7">Pasos para la integración</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgd116df7">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org4a4439d" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org4a4439d">Crear un entorno virtual (opcional)</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org4a4439d">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><p>
Crea un entorno virtual:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   python -m venv env
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Activa el entorno:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   <span style="color: #c099ff;">source</span> env/bin/activate   <span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">En Linux/MacOS</span>
   .\env\Scripts\activate    <span style="color: #7a88cf;"># </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">En Windows</span>
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Instala Django si aún no lo has hecho:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   pip install django
</pre>
</div></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgb71913c" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgb71913c">Crear un proyecto y una aplicación de Django</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgb71913c">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><p>
Crea un nuevo proyecto:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   django-admin startproject mi_proyecto
   <span style="color: #c099ff;">cd</span> mi_proyecto
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Crea una aplicación dentro del proyecto:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   python manage.py startapp mi_app
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Agrega la aplicación al archivo `settings.py`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">INSTALLED_APPS</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  ...
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'mi_app'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgddae0a8" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgddae0a8">Integrar Bootstrap en Django</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgddae0a8">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li>Descarga Bootstrap:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Visita <a href="https://getbootstrap.com/">https://getbootstrap.com/</a> y copia el enlace al CSS y JS.</li>
</ul></li>

<li><p>
Crea un directorio para archivos estáticos en tu aplicación:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   mkdir mi_app/static
   mkdir mi_app/static/css mi_app/static/js mi_app/static/img
</pre>
</div></li>

<li>Agrega los enlaces de Bootstrap al archivo `base.html` (archivo de plantilla base):
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><p>
Crea el archivo `templates/base.html`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">     &lt;<span style="color: #c099ff;">!DOCTYPE</span> html&gt;
     &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">html</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">lang</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"en"</span>&gt;
     &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">head</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">meta</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">charset</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"UTF-8"</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">meta</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">name</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"viewport"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">content</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">title</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">{% block title %}Mi Proyecto{% endblock %}</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">title</span>&gt;
         <span style="color: #7a88cf;">&lt;!-- </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Enlace a Bootstrap</span><span style="color: #7a88cf;"> --&gt;</span>
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">link</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">rel</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"stylesheet"</span>&gt;
     &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">head</span>&gt;
     &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">body</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"container"</span>&gt;
             {% block content %}
             {% endblock %}
         &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span>&gt;
         <span style="color: #7a88cf;">&lt;!-- </span><span style="color: #7a88cf;">Script de Bootstrap</span><span style="color: #7a88cf;"> --&gt;</span>
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">script</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">src</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">script</span>&gt;
     &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">body</span>&gt;
     &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">html</span>&gt;
</pre>
</div></li>
</ul></li>

<li><p>
Configura `settings.py` para buscar archivos estáticos:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">STATIC_URL</span> = <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'/static/'</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">STATICFILES_DIRS</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  BASE_DIR / <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'mi_app/static'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div></li>

<li>Crea una plantilla heredada para una página ejemplo:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><p>
En `mi<sub>app</sub>/templates/mi<sub>app</sub>/index.html`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">     {% extends 'base.html' %}
     {% block title %}Inicio{% endblock %}
     {% block content %}
     &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"text-center"</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bienvenido a mi Proyecto con Bootstrap</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span>&gt;
     &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"btn btn-primary"</span>&gt;Haz clic aqu&#237;&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span>&gt;
     {% endblock %}
</pre>
</div></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgc16fb89" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgc16fb89">Probar el proyecto</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgc16fb89">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li>Modifica `urls.py` en la aplicación para mostrar la página de inicio:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><p>
En `mi<sub>app</sub>/urls.py`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span><span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.urls <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> path
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span><span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> . <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> views

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">urlpatterns</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">''</span>, views.index, name=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">'index'</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span><span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div></li>
</ul></li>

<li><p>
Crea la vista `index` en `mi<sub>app</sub>/views.py`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.shortcuts <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> render

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">index</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> render<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>request, <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'mi_app/index.html'</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Incluye las rutas de la aplicación en `mi<sub>proyecto</sub>/urls.py`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.contrib <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> admin
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.urls <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> path, include

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">urlpatterns</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">[</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'admin/'</span>, admin.site.urls<span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  path<span style="color: #ff995e;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">''</span>, include<span style="color: #ff98a4;">(</span><span style="color: #c3e88d;">'mi_app.urls'</span><span style="color: #ff98a4;">)</span><span style="color: #ff995e;">)</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">]</span>
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Ejecuta el servidor:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-shell">   python manage.py runserver
</pre>
</div></li>

<li>Visita <a href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/">http://127.0.0.1:8000/</a> para ver la página inicial con Bootstrap integrado.</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>


<div id="outline-container-org86bfc74" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="org86bfc74">Código de Flet a Django con Bootstrap</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org86bfc74">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org26f7988" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org26f7988">Requisitos Previos</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org26f7988">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><b><b>Python</b></b> y <b><b>Django</b></b> instalados:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Instalar Django: <code>pip install django</code></li>
<li>Instalar psycopg2: <code>pip install psycopg2</code></li>
</ul></li>
<li>Configurar PostgreSQL:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Crear una base de datos llamada <code>ejemplo</code>.</li>
<li>Configurar un usuario con acceso.</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org3f1f908" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org3f1f908">Crear el Proyecto Django</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org3f1f908">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><p>
Crear un nuevo proyecto:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-bash">   django-admin startproject gestion_personas
   <span style="color: #c099ff;">cd</span> gestion_personas
</pre>
</div></li>

<li><p>
Crear una aplicación:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-bash">   python manage.py startapp personas
</pre>
</div></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgeba327e" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orgeba327e">Configuración del Proyecto Django</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orgeba327e">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org8c1d026" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org8c1d026">Configuración de la Base de Datos en <code>settings.py</code></h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org8c1d026">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">DATABASES</span> = <span style="color: #c099ff;">{</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'default'</span>: <span style="color: #ff995e;">{</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'ENGINE'</span>: <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'django.db.backends.postgresql'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'NAME'</span>: <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'ejemplo'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'USER'</span>: <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'postgres'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'PASSWORD'</span>: <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'tu_password'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'HOST'</span>: <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'localhost'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'PORT'</span>: <span style="color: #c3e88d;">'5432'</span>,
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff995e;">}</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">}</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgf72cb44" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgf72cb44">Definir el Modelo de Persona</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgf72cb44">
<p>
Edita el archivo <code>models.py</code> en la aplicación <code>personas</code>:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-python"><span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">from</span> django.db <span style="color: #c099ff;">import</span> models

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">class</span> <span style="color: #ffc777;">Persona</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>models.Model<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #ff98a4;">nombre</span> = models.CharField<span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span>max_length=100<span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  edad = models.IntegerField<span style="color: #c099ff;">()</span>

<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">def</span> <span style="color: #82aaff;">__str__</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">(</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span><span style="color: #c099ff;">)</span>:
<span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>   <span style="background-color: #2f334d;"> </span>  <span style="color: #c099ff;">return</span> <span style="color: #c099ff;">self</span>.nombre
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org9f55f64" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org9f55f64">Crear y Aplicar Migraciones</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org9f55f64">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-bash">   python manage.py makemigrations personas
   python manage.py migrate
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org5505e30" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org5505e30">Configurar Bootstrap en el Proyecto</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org5505e30">
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><p>
Agregar enlaces de Bootstrap a las plantillas HTML:
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>En cada plantilla que crees, incluye lo siguiente en el `&lt;head&gt;` y al final del `&lt;body&gt;`:</li>
</ul>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">link</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">rel</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"stylesheet"</span>&gt;
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">script</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">src</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">script</span>&gt;
</pre>
</div></li>

<li>Organizar plantillas con una base:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><p>
Crea un archivo `templates/base.html`:
</p>
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">     &lt;<span style="color: #c099ff;">!DOCTYPE</span> html&gt;
     &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">html</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">lang</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"en"</span>&gt;
     &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">head</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">meta</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">charset</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"UTF-8"</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">meta</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">name</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"viewport"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">content</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">title</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">{% block title %}Gesti&#243;n de Personas{% endblock %}</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">title</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">link</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">rel</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"stylesheet"</span>&gt;
     &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">head</span>&gt;
     &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">body</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"container"</span>&gt;
             &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">nav</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light"</span>&gt;
                 &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"navbar-brand"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"/"</span>&gt;Gesti&#243;n Personas&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;
                 &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"collapse navbar-collapse"</span>&gt;
                     &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">ul</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"navbar-nav mr-auto"</span>&gt;
                         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">li</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nav-item"</span>&gt;&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nav-link"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"/"</span>&gt;Lista&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">li</span>&gt;
                         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">li</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nav-item"</span>&gt;&lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nav-link"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"/agregar/"</span>&gt;Agregar&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">li</span>&gt;
                     &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">ul</span>&gt;
                 &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span>&gt;
             &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">nav</span>&gt;
             &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">main</span>&gt;
                 {% block content %}
                 {% endblock %}
             &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">main</span>&gt;
         &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span>&gt;
         &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">script</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">src</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">script</span>&gt;
     &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">body</span>&gt;
     &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">html</span>&gt;
</pre>
</div></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org591ceb8" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org591ceb8">Crear las Plantillas HTML con Bootstrap</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org591ceb8">
<p>
Crea una carpeta <code>templates</code> dentro de la aplicación <code>personas</code> y agrega los siguientes archivos:
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org07f0fbc" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org07f0fbc">Plantilla: <code>lista_personas.html</code></h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org07f0fbc">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">   {% extends 'base.html' %}
   {% block title %}Lista de Personas{% endblock %}
   {% block content %}
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"text-center mt-4"</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Lista de Personas</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span>&gt;
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"/agregar/"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"btn btn-primary mb-3"</span>&gt;Agregar Persona&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">ul</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"list-group"</span>&gt;
       {% for persona in personas %}
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">li</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center"</span>&gt;
               ID: {{ persona.id }} - Nombre: {{ persona.nombre }} - Edad: {{ persona.edad }}
               &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">span</span>&gt;
                   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"/modificar/{{ persona.id }}/"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"btn btn-warning btn-sm"</span>&gt;Modificar&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;
                   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">href</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"/eliminar/{{ persona.id }}/"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"btn btn-danger btn-sm"</span>&gt;Eliminar&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">a</span>&gt;
               &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">span</span>&gt;
           &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">li</span>&gt;
       {% endfor %}
   &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">ul</span>&gt;
   {% endblock %}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org9aab0dc" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org9aab0dc">Plantilla: <code>agregar_persona.html</code></h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org9aab0dc">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">   {% extends 'base.html' %}
   {% block title %}Agregar Persona{% endblock %}
   {% block content %}
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"text-center mt-4"</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Agregar Persona</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span>&gt;
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">form</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">method</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"POST"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"mt-3"</span>&gt;
       {% csrf_token %}
       &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"mb-3"</span>&gt;
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">for</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nombre"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"form-label"</span>&gt;Nombre&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span>&gt;
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">input</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"text"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"form-control"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">id</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nombre"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">name</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nombre"</span>&gt;
       &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span>&gt;
       &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"mb-3"</span>&gt;
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">for</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"edad"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"form-label"</span>&gt;Edad&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span>&gt;
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">input</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"number"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"form-control"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">id</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"edad"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">name</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"edad"</span>&gt;
       &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span>&gt;
       &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"submit"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"btn btn-success"</span>&gt;Agregar&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span>&gt;
   &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">form</span>&gt;
   {% endblock %}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org7f1aeb4" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org7f1aeb4">Plantilla: <code>modificar_persona.html</code></h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-org7f1aeb4">
<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-html">   {% extends 'base.html' %}
   {% block title %}Modificar Persona{% endblock %}
   {% block content %}
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"text-center mt-4"</span>&gt;<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Modificar Persona</span>&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">h1</span>&gt;
   &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">form</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">method</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"POST"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"mt-3"</span>&gt;
       {% csrf_token %}
       &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"mb-3"</span>&gt;
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">for</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nombre"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"form-label"</span>&gt;Nombre&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span>&gt;
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">input</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"text"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"form-control"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">id</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nombre"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">name</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"nombre"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">value</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"{{ persona.nombre }}"</span>&gt;
       &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span>&gt;
       &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"mb-3"</span>&gt;
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">for</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"edad"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"form-label"</span>&gt;Edad&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">label</span>&gt;
           &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">input</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"number"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"form-control"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">id</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"edad"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">name</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"edad"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">value</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"{{ persona.edad }}"</span>&gt;
       &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">div</span>&gt;
       &lt;<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">type</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"submit"</span> <span style="color: #ff98a4;">class</span>=<span style="color: #c3e88d;">"btn btn-warning"</span>&gt;Modificar&lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">button</span>&gt;
   &lt;/<span style="color: #82aaff;">form</span>&gt;
   {% endblock %}
</pre>
</div>
</div>
</div>
